---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="The simplest way to create Semantic, Scripted EPUB books." />
    <title>SEED — Simple EPUB Editor</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="content">
      <div id="logo">
        <img src="/img/RobotInaBox-trademark_logo.png" alt="RobotInaBox" />
      </div>
      <h1>SEED</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Simple EPUB Editor</p>
      <p class="description">The simplest way to create Semantic, Scripted EPUB books.</p>

      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <h2>Plain Text Input</h2>
          <p>Write in Markdown, Asciidoc, Textile, Org Mode, LaTeX, or Fountain. No markup learning curve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h2>Valid EPUB 3.2</h2>
          <p>Generates standards-compliant EPUB files with proper structure and accessibility metadata.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h2>No Installation</h2>
          <p>Runs entirely in your browser. Works offline. Nothing to install or update.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/seed/" class="btn-primary">Launch SEED</a>
        <a href="/docs/introduction/" class="btn-secondary">Read the docs</a>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <p>© 2025 <a href="https://robotinabox.com">RobotInaBox</a></p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  body {
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #fff;
    color: #111;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  #content {
    max-width: 40em;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 3em 1.5em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  #logo img {
    width: 8em;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.2em;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1em;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 3em;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(11em, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 3em;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature h2 {
    font-size: 0.9em;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #555;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1em;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 4em;
  }

  a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75em 2em;
    border-radius: 2em;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #333;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    color: #111;
    padding: 0.75em 2em;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 2em;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #999;
  }

  footer {
    font-size: 0.75em;
    color: #999;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  footer a {
    color: #999;
  }
</style>
